{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot depicts a waterfront industrial scene with a large, dark-colored crane dominating the left side of the frame. The crane, labeled 'SCHNITZER STEEL', stands over a network of wooden piers and a conveyor belt system extending into the water. The conveyor belt appears to be transporting scrap metal or similar materials, evidenced by the large pile of debris at its end. Reflections of the structures shimmer on the calm, dark blue water. In the background, a distant cityscape with buildings and additional cranes is visible under a bright blue sky with wispy clouds. The overall scene suggests a bustling industrial port area focused on recycling or material processing.",
